img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa604200dd2eaf73f89224035c30418f86c2ce2","tid":247283,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T00:25:53.000Z","msg":"嘩.....叫政事台班友點跟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"083ecf7c3e66d0ef54c452af295a8afffaa74516","tid":247283,"uid":2707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T01:48:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好咁易一嘢就為自己支持嘅事物上頭，仆都仆唔切標籤人乜乜乜<br />\n上面就係好例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢講到咁實，選嗰個就當然唔會係佢啦<br />\n但連呢單嘢都可以覺今是而昨非，想博咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩叫連呢單嘢都可以自今是而昨非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔講以為係毓民做主動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n碌撚一早講到明授權呢條友做嘅任何嘢，原來而家又唔關事嗱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n建議一眾想準備盲撐嘅人聽唔足節目就唔好亂撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時下台階其實就好易砌，但總係要將自己嘅退路切斷晒先安落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc74a680fa08d3fd146764ccc0998a62e314eff4","tid":247283,"uid":2707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T01:49:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩.....叫政事台班友點跟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家其實都係當娛樂新聞咁睇，關人撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f02572564054bb7efe79ff49e5aeaaf46ea6f0","tid":247283,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T02:03:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>根本呢個救生員先係挑起呢次風波既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n驚死黃洋達同陳雲唔還拖，係咁煽風點火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">出左十宗罪咁既人，全撚部都係啲九唔搭八 雞毛蒜皮既野</span></blockquote><br />\n隔離post好多人j緊喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢度真係抵畀人話係本民青討論區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n與其話J倒不如話係恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢度的確係多本民青支持者<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但由於唔妥陳雲既唔只係本民青<br />\n所以見到陳雲派系既負面消息，大家當然踴躍食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n呢樣真<br />\n但仲盲撐碌撚/本民青真係好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點都好過撐熱狗云伯堆垃圾既"},{"pid":"c2b16b6d97332a3c02658bf672b7ba7f66a89a55","tid":247283,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T02:54:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連堂主都有得睇了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁椰子巴打有得睇未？"},{"pid":"1d5444d78b3bf9ffc0026a20a7cd93a03007e553","tid":247283,"uid":39221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T02:57:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩.....叫政事台班友點跟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s